{"tid":1541740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌啦！！！ 0/5呀！！！","createTime":"2019-09-04T15:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:54:16.000Z","uid":193667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f5db1a70548c5b3b93a2b1cc27e79fe40a13a20e","tid":1541740,"uid":193667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"仆你個街 呢條柒婆講大話當食生菜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初又話唔選特首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n選到又話市民唔滿意佢嘅話會辭職 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解今次我要信呢條大話精？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「徹回」呢兩隻字仲要係用<br />\n百萬香港人嘅汗水時間,<br />\n成千位被捕手足前途,<br />\n同埋咁多位烈士生命換返嚟<br />\n一個大話精所謂&quot;promise&quot;根本唔值咁嘅價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家唔好就咁收貨<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算林鄭收皮 我都唔收貨呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"0e7f3275569f7870d473429f7180b71d8415c122","tid":1541740,"uid":306286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:54:06.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc8a8831a4db05b597d904e1cf68be399f02300","tid":1541740,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n<br />\n分別在於:<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n8人離世<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-s